        <label>make winter's reign</label>
        <description>A rod of blue steel adorned with a crown of crystal shards. The touch of this staff never warms, as if to remind the bearer of it's icy sovereignty. The power of the staff is two-fold - it greatly augments the innate magical power of a mage and is able to create a hailstorm in any environment. The power of the staff has its price - when held, the staff will drain heat and energy from the holder and, if held by a mage, expands this effect to the surrounding atmosphere. Only mages are able to project the power of this staff.\n\nThis weapon is enchanted and provides additional benefits to trained mages and fighters:\nMax Energy: +80\nAbility Cooldown: -30%\nArcane Resistance: +20%\nArcane Damage: +50%\n\nAbility: Hailstorm</description>
